---
import DocsLayout from '../../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import Checklist from '../../../../components/Checklist.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="BACKLOG: GreenScape" description="8 tickets from empty directory to live site.">
  <h1 class="mb-8">Backlog: GreenScape Landscaping</h1>

  <!-- Ticket 1 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">setup</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: S</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 1: Project Setup</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Create the GitHub repository, copy CLAUDE.md and BACKLOG.md, set up labels, Issues, and Project board.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "GitHub repository exists with CLAUDE.md and BACKLOG.md committed",
      "GitHub labels created: setup, frontend, deploy",
      "GitHub Issues created for all tickets in this backlog",
      "GitHub Project board created with columns: To Do, In Progress, Done",
      "All Issues added to the Project board in the To Do column",
      ".gitignore includes node_modules, dist, .env",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 2 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">setup</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: S</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T1</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 2: Development Environment</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Initialise React + Vite with Tailwind CSS. Create Makefile and content data file.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "make dev starts the Vite development server on localhost:5173",
      "Browser shows 'GreenScape Landscaping' as the page title",
      "Tailwind CSS is working (utility class renders correctly)",
      "make lint runs ESLint without errors",
      "src/data/content.js exists with placeholder content for all sections",
      "Repository structure matches CLAUDE.md",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 3 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">frontend</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: M</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T2</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 3: Site Layout & Navigation</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Sticky header, navigation, footer. Responsive with mobile hamburger menu.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "Header displays business name and navigation links",
      "Clicking a nav link smooth-scrolls to the section",
      "Header remains visible when scrolling (sticky)",
      "Footer displays copyright year and contact info",
      "Mobile: navigation collapses into hamburger menu",
      "Desktop: navigation links displayed horizontally",
      "Colours and fonts match the design tokens in CLAUDE.md",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 4 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">frontend</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: M</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T3</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 4: Hero & Services Section</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Hero with headline, tagline, CTA. Six service cards in responsive grid.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "Hero displays business name, tagline, and 'Get in Touch' CTA",
      "CTA button scrolls to the Contact section",
      "Hero has background image or colour matching design",
      "6 service cards with icon placeholder, name, and description",
      "Grid: 1 column mobile, 2 tablet, 3 desktop",
      "All text from content.js, not hardcoded",
      "No horizontal scrolling on any screen size",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 5 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">frontend</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: M</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T4</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 5: Testimonials & About Sections</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">4 testimonial cards with star ratings. About section with photo placeholder and bio.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "4 testimonials with quote text, name, suburb, and 5-star visual",
      "Testimonials visually distinct (different background or card style)",
      "About section has photo placeholder and 2–3 paragraphs",
      "About text max ~700px for readability",
      "Star ratings are visual (icons or CSS), not text '5/5'",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 6 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">frontend</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: M</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T5</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 6: Service Area & Contact Sections</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Suburb list. Contact with clickable phone and email links. No contact form.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "Service area displays all 10 suburbs from the PRD",
      "Contact shows phone, email, address, business hours",
      "Phone is a tel: link — opens dialer on mobile",
      "Email is a mailto: link — opens email client",
      "Business hours clearly formatted",
      "No contact form exists (anti-scope)",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 7 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">frontend</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: S</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T6</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 7: SEO & Meta Tags</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Page title, meta description, Open Graph tags, semantic HTML, heading hierarchy.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "Page title contains 'GreenScape Landscaping' and 'Melbourne'",
      "Meta description exists (150–160 characters)",
      "Open Graph tags: og:title, og:description, og:image, og:url",
      "Only one <h1> element on the page",
      "Heading hierarchy logical: h1 → h2 → h3",
      "Semantic HTML: nav, main, section, footer",
      "All images have alt text",
      "Lighthouse SEO score 90+",
    ]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Ticket 8 -->
  <div class="border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">deploy</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-bg-muted text-text-secondary">Size: S</span>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-primary-bg text-primary">Deps: T7</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ticket 8: Deploy</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-4">Deploy to Netlify free tier. Verify live site matches dev.</p>
    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Acceptance Criteria</h4>
    <Checklist items={[
      "Site deployed to a live URL",
      "All sections load correctly on the live site",
      "Images load (not broken)",
      "Phone tel: link works on a real mobile phone",
      "Responsive on the live URL (check on actual phone)",
      "Lighthouse performance score 80+",
      "Lighthouse SEO score 90+",
    ]} />
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
